reviews.text: Food was good. I was upset that the waiter sweetened my tea for me because he emptied the entire bottle of simple syrup into my tea and it was too sweet to drink. Please don't decide this for me, let me add the syrup to my taste. Even my kids thought it was too sweet and they are kids.
Go during lunch time. Get the chicken soup. You get the full portion. Dinner is a tad on the expensive side but still good. Go for the garlic marinated beef.

Korean BBQ in basement; good beef but pricy. Not many appetizer dishes. The hot and spicy seafood soup is disappointing - no seafood flavor except spicy. The Korean rice cake and dumpling soup is another disappointment - tasteless. Free refill of egg kimchi mixture and liquid cheese.
Good korean bbq. Meat are fresh

really enjoyed my visit, customer service was always avaliable and easy to get. ventilation system works well. Nice storage space for bags under seat. meat is ok quality, no issues with veg, manager is friendly and helpful.

There is space for the baby chair, you are presented with tissues wipes etc. this is better quality than all you can eat bbq. the beer tower is very handy

reviews.text: Second time I've been here. I prefer this location because it's not as crowded as their other locations nearby. This way I know I will get better service because there are more staff available to serve my table. =)
Inexpensive BBQ lunch sets, and fast service. Unlimited side dish and appetizers. But some areas are not very clean/dry. Leaking from the AC, maybe.

I was in Hong Kong for a couple of weeks and want to try a Korean restaurant, this want was recommended by a friend and it was pretty good experience for myself and for my family.This type restaurant  you choose the meat or sea food etc. to cook on a  gas powered hot plate.The place was clean and tidy, staff was helpful and pleasant. Definitely recommend just for the mocktails .
nice and worth the price
Good!

result.name: 炑八韓烤 (太子店)

reviews.text:
旺角炑八"韓烤 
有幸被  邀請去旺角炑/\"韓烤吃晚飯，同朋友2人，我朋友說之前吃過，味道很好!想再吃，她說上次耒在門口排隊，很多人排了很久才有位
    昨日因不是星期六，日吧，不用排隊有位。入到門口見個招牌很醒目，牆壁兩邊都有但唔同，很特別。望落有舒服的感覺。
    進去見到D侍應很有禮貌，招呼我們坐下，坐位很舒適，鋪面清潔簡單，比人有一種舒服親切的感受。
   我們 叫了一個套餐，還有一個王者牛肋骨。先來點前菜，有沙律,泡菜,羅蔔,海澡....·五花八門的配菜，
   好有特色的菜沙律，酸酸甜甜，好似有 橘子味 , 檸檬味·總而然知豐富你味覺。泡菜爽脆味道也很好。最好的還有牛肋骨，燒烤恰到好處(有侍應幫你)，入口有 鬆軟甘香，那種感覺非筆墨很形容!是開心! 窩心!滿足!的感覺。
有五花腩，肥牛,雞肉,牛扒,選料上乘，腌制味道很好，問過侍應，她說是秘方。另你吃過後好想再去的感覺，有時間你們也可去吃，不要 錯過的好去處。
下午茶不錯 人不太多 价格可接受 食物水準合格以上

午餐抵食 冇加一 cp值高
而且不時會轉下餐牌
沒有收加一服務費，有高速wifi提供
食親都好正
